data.description: Incredible opportunity to own this newly updated ranch-style home in a fantastic Highlands Ranch location with only one original owner. Step inside to a gorgeous open layout with fresh interior paint, new carpeting, newly refinished gleaming hardwood floors, all new appliances, water heater 2017, furnace 2020 and radon mitigation 2023. The spacious living room boasts a fireplace and glass door leading to the private backyard and a large deck with a mature tree nearby offering plenty of shade and privacy. Home chefs will love the brand new kitchen remodel boasting new stainless steel appliances, new white quartz countertops, pretty gray subway tile backsplash, new under-mount sink & faucet, and great panty to house your kitchen essentials. A large dining room and peninsula island provides ample seating for large gatherings. Three generous-sized main-level bedrooms, including the primary retreat with brand new carpeting, bright and sunny en-suite bath, and a large walk-in closet & linen closet. Main-level laundry room makes laundry day easy. More living space found in the fully finished basement with an additional bedroom with a nearby bath, and a family room that could easily be used as a home office or addition bedroom. Home is ADA compliant. Home also has a new roof! Rare-to-find 3-car garage great for vehicles and gear! Great Highlands Ranch location just a block to E Fork Trail to enjoy the great outdoors, walking distance to local elementary school, shops, Starbucks, & King Soopers, and quick access to C-470 to easily get you to the mountains or downtowns. This move-in-ready gem is a must-see and needs nothing for you to do but move right in and call it home! ***NEW ROOF INSTALLED NOVEMBER 2023 WITH TRANSFERABLE 5 YEAR WARRANTY***
